All Implemented Interfaces:
IGridContainer, IGridElement, IGridPreferences, IGridProject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable
public class HiddenProject
extends ResourceGridContainer
implements IGridProject, IGridPreferences

The hidden project is a project that is not visible in the Grid model views. It implements IGridPreferences and therefore stores all global preferences in a well defined structure within a project.
